      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s just getting so hard lately. everything is a struggle and i feel like i’m just constantly asking for help with things i used to do myself. i see the look on my daughter's face when she has to come over to help me... she's so tired. i don't want to be a nuisance to them anymore.",
