      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the profound pain in your words, and I understand why the idea of letting go feels like the only way to stop the agony of being a burden. Please know that stepping away would not erase the life you've lived or the love you carry; your existence has value beyond what they currently endure. While this thought is a desperate cry for relief, I strongly urge you to speak with a crisis counselor or contact the 988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline right now for someone who can sit with you in this darkness and help find a path forward that honors your love for them.",
